{"tid":2352824,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求救！朝早俾個風扇整到步電腦，開機有問題。","createTime":"2021-01-04T09:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T11:20:57.000Z","uid":237121,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f860319d038f8a28d29bb1b97f8e428a268817b4","tid":2352824,"uid":237121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T09:43:51.000Z","msg":"朝早俾個風扇整到個電腦頂，之後就開唔到機，試過幾次都係咁。部主機係開到，但係keyboard，Mouse同埋個mon就冇反應。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/anmBro9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FanmBro9.png&h=1ed99a39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67381ff2581b09a380fa818690f0309a5ca56458","tid":2352824,"uid":335003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:00:59.000Z","msg":"可能啲嘢鬆咗，留意下開機有無 debug 燈著。<br />\n<br />\nram,mouse,keyboard,display card, mon 線全部抆起清塵重插。 (因為你唔知邊樣鬆)<br />\n<br />\ncpu 正常就好難鬆，而且要有散熱膏先好搞，所以就有佢先。除非 debug 燈係著 cpu 訧一定要整。<br />\n<br />\n順有睇下啲插線嘅 hdmi/ usb 線頭之類有無變形/爛。"},{"pid":"617b0905037f146a83a7e1f480ad0aa0f4f3bd83","tid":2352824,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67381ff2581b09a380fa818690f0309a5ca56458","tid":2352824,"uid":335003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:00:59.000Z","msg":"可能啲嘢鬆咗，留意下開機有無 debug 燈著。<br />\n<br />\nram,mouse,keyboard,display card, mon 線全部抆起清塵重插。 (因為你唔知邊樣鬆)<br />\n<br />\ncpu 正常就好難鬆，而且要有散熱膏先好搞，所以就有佢先。除非 debug 燈係著 cpu 訧一定要整。<br />\n<br />\n順有睇下啲插線嘅 hdmi/ usb 線頭之類有無變形/爛。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:10:25.000Z","msg":"我睇唔到佢塊板有debug燈呢樣嘢"},{"pid":"01a81e6ac9e9dc57784f3084b52916c84a964a08","tid":2352824,"uid":18012,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:30:51.000Z","msg":"咁多人用 intel原廠風扇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f5a80e22840856b5c1f431ef2e05ebeacedb8f","tid":2352824,"uid":237121